Introduction In this tutorial, we show how to get virtual memory information of the computer in Java application with OSHI library.
Add OSHI library to the Java project To use OSHI Java library in the Gradle build project, add the following dependency into the build.gradle file. compile group: &#39;com.github.oshi&#39;, name: &#39;oshi-core&#39;, version: &#39;5.3.4&#39;
